query:
INSERT INTO trip_travelers (tripId, name, identifier, sortOrder, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 2 as tripId, name, identifier, sortOrder, NOW() as createdAt, NOW() as updatedAt
FROM trip_travelers
WHERE tripId = 1;

INSERT INTO checklist_items (tripId, title, category, completed, dueDate, notes, owner, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT 2 as tripId, title, category, completed, dueDate, notes, owner, NOW() as createdAt, NOW() as updatedAt
FROM checklist_items
WHERE tripId = 1;
